      <header class="features-item">
        <h2 lang="en">Give your users the latest version of the web</h2>
        <h2 lang="zh">为你的用户提供最新的web技术</h2>
        <!-- <p>With the Crosswalk Project, your app will render the same across every Android 4.0 device, so you can simultaneously test on less devices and know your apps works in more places.</p> -->
      </header>
      <div class="features-item">
        <h4 lang="en" class="features-heading">Provide a Google Chrome-like in-app&nbsp;browser</h4>
        <h4 lang="zh" class="features-heading">提供一个类似于Google Chrome的内嵌浏览器</h4>
        <hr class="features-pointer" />
        <p lang="en">In-app browsers are used more than the default Android browser. Give your users the latest version of the web by using the Crosswalk Project as your app’s embedded browser.</p>
        <p lang="zh">内嵌浏览器的应用场景比Android默认浏览器更多。将Crosswalk作为应用的内嵌浏览器，为你的用户提供最新的web技术。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-item">
