        <hr class="features-pointer" />
        <p lang="en">The Crosswalk Project supports exactly what you’d expect from a WebView based on Google Chromium and Blink. Easily make your users’ browser and experience great.</p>
        <p lang="zh">如你所期望的一样，Crosswalk完全支持基于Google Chromium和Blink内核的WebView的强大功能，轻松提升用户的浏览及使用体验。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-item">
