        <hr class="features-pointer" />
        <p lang="en">As more browsers support performance monitoring <abbr>API</abbr>s, the more accurate your performance measurements become. The Crosswalk Project helps increase your sample size.</p>
        <p lang="zh">当越来越多的浏览器都在使用性能监控<abbr>API</abbr>，你的应用的性能度量变得越来越精确。Crosswalk可以帮助你增加样本的数量。</p>
